# ============================================================
# Client Workspace — Environment Variables
# ============================================================
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in your real values from 1Password (or your password manager)
# 3. NEVER commit the .env file — it's blocked by .gitignore
# 4. Claude Code CANNOT read .env files — this is a security feature
#
# !! CRITICAL — READ THIS !!
# These keys are YOUR property. YOU generate them. YOU store them.
# Keys go: your platform account → your 1Password → this .env file.
# NOWHERE ELSE. Not Slack. Not email. Not Claude chat. Not a Google Doc.
# If a key appears anywhere other than 1Password or this file,
# REVOKE IT IMMEDIATELY and generate a new one.
# ============================================================

# Claude API (only needed if using API billing instead of subscription)
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# OpenAI (only if using embeddings or Whisper transcription)
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...

# Google (only if connecting Google Workspace via API)
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
# GOOGLE_CLIENT_SECRET=
# GOOGLE_REFRESH_TOKEN=
